Ultimately the questions remain—What power do CCPSA elected officials have to enforce oversight when they are required to work with the Chief they are supposed to be overseeing? What power do they have to enforce rules beyond termination (like seeking a murder trial)?

The NBA Coaches Carosel of Police Chief’s from Baltimore, Chicago, Oakland, New York, Dallas and LA has proven that simply changing Police leadership is ineffective. Additionally, oversight of police rules (part of GAPA/CCPSA) is already something City Council already does.
